<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bear-in-mind-bear-in-mind-that">bear … in mind / bear in mind that ...</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>把…记在心里；记住…：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’ll bear the beautiful girl in mind forever. 
他将永远记住那位美丽的姑娘。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bear in mind that nothing is impossible.
记住没有什么是不可能的。</p></div></div>